The Sheriff of Baltimore County shall receive an annual salary of:
$75,000 for calendar year 2007;
$80,000 for calendar year 2008;
$85,000 for calendar year 2009; and
$90,000 for calendar year 2010 and each subsequent calendar year.

The Sheriff of Carroll County shall receive an annual salary as follows:
$71,532 beginning December 5, 2006;
$72,963 beginning December 4, 2007;
$74,422 beginning December 9, 2008; and
$75,910 beginning December 8, 2009, and thereafter.

The Sheriff of Kent County shall receive a salary of:
$67,000 for the calendar year 2009;
$68,000 for the calendar year 2010;
$82,000 for the calendar year 2011;
$83,000 for the calendar year 2012;
$84,000 for the calendar year 2013; and
$85,000 for the calendar year 2014 and each calendar year thereafter.

Neither the Sheriff of Prince George's County nor any of the Sheriff's deputies shall conduct criminal investigations, except:
In matters concerning the Sheriff's department;
On request of the courts;
As necessary for the administration and enforcement of casino night permits as authorized by the county governing body; or
In investigations arising out of or incident to normally assigned duties, including those duties authorized by the county governing body under paragraph (8)(i)6 of this subsection.

The annual salary of the Sheriff of St. Mary's County shall be:
$76,000 for the calendar year 2007;
$78,000 for the calendar year 2008;
$80,000 for the calendar year 2009; and
$82,000 for the calendar year 2010.
